name.k: LEGO®ニンジャゴー ローニンの影

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: Jump in and save the ninjas!

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Goofy banter, diverting puzzles, wall-to-wall action—we couldn’t ask for more from a LEGO Ninjago game. Using the warriors’ trademark weapons and elemental moves, you’ll battle the nefarious Ronin and his crew across Chen’s Island, the Toxic Bogs, and other familiar settings. Even if you’ve never seen the Masters of Spinjitzu animated series, these hilarious heroes and their kid-friendly shenanigans are guaranteed to win you over.
